### PawsHope Backend - Sample API calls (VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP)
@host = http://localhost:4000
@adminToken = paste-admin-jwt-after-login
@userToken = paste-user-jwt-after-login

### Health check
GET {{host}}/api/health

### --- AUTH ---
### Register
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "password": "demo12345",
  "fullName": "Demo User",
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "phone": "0901234567"
}

### Login admin
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "admin", "password": "admin123" }

### Login user1
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "user1", "password": "user123" }

### /me
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### --- RESCUE ---
### Public stats (frontend đang gọi cái này)
GET {{host}}/api/rescue-reports/public-stats

### Create rescue report (anonymous)
POST {{host}}/api/rescue-reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reporterName": "Người dân Hà Nội",
  "reporterPhone": "0987654321",
  "locationText": "Đầu phố Bà Triệu, Q. Hai Bà Trưng, Hà Nội",
  "description": "Một bé mèo con bị thương ở chân, đang nằm dưới gầm xe."
}

### Track by code (thay code thực tế)
GET {{host}}/api/rescue-reports/track/RP-2026-7260

### List rescue (admin only)
GET {{host}}/api/rescue-reports?status=Pending&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update status (assign volunteer)
PATCH {{host}}/api/rescue-reports/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{ "status": "In Progress", "assignedTo": 2 }

### --- PETS / KENNELS ---
### List pets (public)
GET {{host}}/api/pets?species=Cat&status=Available&page=1&limit=10

### Get pet
GET {{host}}/api/pets/1

### Create pet (admin)
POST {{host}}/api/pets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Miu Vàng",
  "species": "Cat",
  "breed": "Mèo ta",
  "ageMonths": 6,
  "status": "Available",
  "description": "Vào trạm sau cứu hộ.",
  "kennelId": 2
}

### List kennels
GET {{host}}/api/kennels

### --- ADOPTIONS ---
### Apply (user)
POST {{host}}/api/adoptions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{ "petId": 1, "notes": "Tôi đã có kinh nghiệm nuôi mèo 5 năm." }

### My adoptions
GET {{host}}/api/adoptions/my
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### All adoptions (admin)
GET {{host}}/api/adoptions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Approve adoption (transactional - đổi pet status & reject các đơn khác)
PATCH {{host}}/api/adoptions/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{ "status": "Approved", "notes": "Hồ sơ ổn, hẹn hôm sau bàn giao." }

### --- PRODUCTS / CART / ORDERS ---
### List products
GET {{host}}/api/products

### Add to cart
POST {{host}}/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{ "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }

### View cart
GET {{host}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Checkout (giảm stock, tạo order, xoá cart - tất cả trong 1 transaction)
POST {{host}}/api/orders/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{ "shippingAddress": "123 Lê Lợi, Q.1, TP.HCM" }

### My orders
GET {{host}}/api/orders/my
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Update order status (admin)
PATCH {{host}}/api/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{ "status": "Shipped" }

### --- DONATIONS ---
### Donate money (anonymous OK)
POST {{host}}/api/donations/money
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "donorName": "Anh Trung",
  "amount": 500000,
  "method": "MoMo",
  "purpose": "Giúp bé Miu Vàng phẫu thuật"
}

### Donate items
POST {{host}}/api/donations/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "donorName": "Chị Lan",
  "itemName": "Thức ăn hạt cho chó",
  "category": "Food",
  "quantity": "10 kg"
}

### Donation stats
GET {{host}}/api/donations/stats

### --- VOLUNTEERS ---
### Apply
POST {{host}}/api/volunteer-applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Phạm Anh Tuấn",
  "email": "tuan@example.com",
  "phone": "0905555444",
  "skills": "Đã chăm sóc 3 bé mèo, có xe máy",
  "reasonToJoin": "Muốn giúp đỡ cộng đồng"
}

### List shifts
GET {{host}}/api/shifts

### Register shift (volunteer/admin)
POST {{host}}/api/volunteer-schedules
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{ "shiftId": 1, "workDate": "2026-05-20" }

### My schedules
GET {{host}}/api/volunteer-schedules/my
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### --- EXPENSES (admin) ---
### Create expense
POST {{host}}/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "category": "Medical",
  "amount": 1500000,
  "description": "Tiền thuốc và truyền nước cho bé Miu Vàng",
  "expenseDate": "2026-05-13"
}

### Expense summary
GET {{host}}/api/expenses/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### --- NOTIFICATIONS ---
GET {{host}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Unread count
GET {{host}}/api/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### --- USERS (admin) ---
GET {{host}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Validation error example (thiếu reporterPhone, locationText quá ngắn)
POST {{host}}/api/rescue-reports
Content-Type: application/json

{ "locationText": "x" }
